             {:href "/blog/structure-vs-interpretation.blog"}
             "Structure vs Interpretation"]
            " (why separating structure from meaning matters)"]
           [:li
            [:a
             {:href "/blog/ast-higher-dimensional-datom-streams.blog"}
             "AST as Higher Dimensional Construction of Datom Streams"]
            " (how complex computation emerges from simple tuples)"]
           [:li
            [:a {:href "/dao-db.chp"} "DaoDB"]
            " (the database that makes datoms universal)"]]]]]}
